  <Dialog id="0" name="MND_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}It's the last day of our school trip...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}We'll be leaving Kyoto by bullet train[n]this afternoon. I'm free until then.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1581 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}{f 5 21 1 10}Okay, everyone! You all remember when we're meeting at Kyoto Station, right?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1581 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}{f 5 21 1 10}You better make sure you're on time. If any one of you is late, I'm the one who pays the price.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}I thought Kyoto was gonna blow, but it actually wasn't that bad.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
